            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1" xml:lang="heb">
                <p>כי<lb/>אני<lb/>יהה<lb/>שמו</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>For I am. YHH his name.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>The first two lines, "For I am", appear on the first of the nine facets on both
                    of the rings. The second two lines, "YHH his name", appear on the fourth facet
                    of the first ring and the fifth facet of the second ring. These were the only
                    two understood facets of the rings.</p>
            </div>
